Release 2.5.2-1.1 Start 27/04/2023 End 31/07/2024
- 15/10/2023
01. Fixed scrobbling button to allow love and unlove
- 04/04/2024
02. Updated INSTALL file with list of packages to be installed for RPM and
    Debian systems
- 10/04/2024
03. Use SIGUSR1, SIGUSR2 to turn on, off love scrobble button
- 25/04/2024
04. Added packaging files for debian, rpm packaging using Open Build Service
05. Updated INSTALL, README files for building on MacOS
- 28/07/2024
06. mac/macnotify.mm: Fixed crash on macos when output device is changed
07. mpd-interface/mpdconnections.h: fixed "Unsupported URI scheme" error
    message in mpd log (incorrect lsinfo command)
08. mpd-interface/mpdconnections.cpp: Increased constConnTimer value to 10000,
    constSocketCommsTimeout to 4000, constConnTimer to 10000
09. mpd-interface/mpdconnections.cpp: added constSocketDataTimeout=2000
10. mpd-interface/mpdconnections.cpp: Changed [Radio Streams] to Radio-Streams
11. mpd-interface/mpdconnections.cpp: Create MPD_HOST, MUSIC_DIR files in
    $HOME/.config/cantata
12. playlists/dynamicplaylists.cpp: Create MPD_HOST env variable
13. mpd-interface/mpdconnections.cpp: fixed multiple reconnects from power
    management code
14. mpd-interface/mpdconnections.cpp: removed dead code
15. scrobbling/scrobblinglove.cpp: replaced mpc_o with cantata-mpc
- 01/08/2024
16. ffmpeginput.cpp: fix compilation for libavutil old channel layout
17. ffmpeginput.cpp: updated for new channel layout
18. gui/playbacksettings.cpp, gui/playbacksettings.ui, gui/settings.cpp,
    gui/settings.h, mpd-interface/mpdconnection.cpp: Unhardcode duration after
    which prev button seeks to start of audio
19. Add options to move tracks at beginning and end of playqueue
- 16/08/2024
20. added scrobbling.md, aux-scripts directory
